 1016 format (//' level',i4,' closed.')                                 lecd-182
 1017 format (//' there are only 20 kind of programmed observables'//'  lecd-183
     1for other kinds, introduce a negative number and, later, their deslecd-184
     2cription.')                                                       lecd-185
